Comment: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:58.79,INJP,1,0,0,0,karaoke,朧月夜　剣の鋭さ潜め
Comment: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:10.74,INJP,2,0,0,0,karaoke,暗夜　霞み揺蕩う
Comment: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:17.39,INJP,3,0,0,0,karaoke,恋しさ堪え
Comment: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:23.06,INJP,4,0,0,0,karaoke,春の宴絢爛に
Comment: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:29.15,INJP,5,0,0,0,karaoke,藤に彩られよ　山野
Comment: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:40.70,INJP,6,0,0,0,karaoke,菜の花に染め上がれ　大地
Comment: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:46.76,INJP,6,0,0,0,karaoke,永久に咲く花は無し
Comment: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:52.71,INJP,6,0,0,0,karaoke,あはれいと恋し
Comment: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:59.01,INJP,6,0,0,0,karaoke,冬の君よ　月の如く
Comment: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:05.27,INJP,6,0,0,0,karaoke,その背を永久に追う
Comment: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:58.79,INCN,1,0,0,0,karaoke,胧月夜兮敛剑锋
Comment: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:10.74,INCN,2,0,0,0,karaoke,暗夜沉兮霞影朦
Comment: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:17.39,INCN,3,0,0,0,karaoke,抑相思兮寸心藏
Comment: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:23.06,INCN,4,0,0,0,karaoke,启春宴兮极华芳
Comment: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:29.15,INCN,5,0,0,0,karaoke,紫藤流彩兮被山野
Comment: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:40.70,INCN,6,0,0,0,karaoke,芸薹灼灼兮染大荒
Comment: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:46.76,INCN,6,0,0,0,karaoke,叹繁花兮靡有常
Comment: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:52.71,INCN,6,0,0,0,karaoke,惹哀怜兮思未央
Comment: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:59.01,INCN,6,0,0,0,karaoke,冬之君兮皎如月
